ActSpecial Economic Measures Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Venezuela) Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the SPECIAL ECONOMIC MEASURES (VENEZUELA) REGULATIONS in order to add fourteen (14) individuals to the Schedule of listed persons under the Regulations in which any person in Canada or Canadians outside of Canada are thereby prohibited from dealing in the property of, entering into transactions with, providing services to, transferring property to, or otherwise making goods available to listed persons.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2025-0001 Publication Date: 2025-01-29
AttachmentsAttachment
